python-bugzilla (0.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * fetch_bug_xml() now have optional parameter for encoding if not returned
    by bugzilla
  * update_bugs() - new function to make mass modification on bugs
  * parse_bug_xml() now converts unprintable characters to '?' by default
  * minor pylint warnings cleanup

